TextBody:
Hello,

You can uninstall the client from the server in "System Configuration > Client uninstall".
Or this can be done manually on the the computer from the control pannel.
Or run the command below in the command line.
msiexec.exe /x <PATH to MSI file> /qn REBOOT=ReallySuppress

Kind regards
__________________
Andrei Pop | Technical Support Engineer
Netwrix Endpoint Protector
